{
  "stem": "20848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was a terrible, terrible time, because we were all so scared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were already halfway de-humanized, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'm sure we were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the manhole opened up and we saw the guns pointed our way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we thought, well that's it, you know, the Germans have come to get us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Believe it or not, it was the Warsaw Ghetto fighters, the young people came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I will never forget that as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were very young, they were 16, 17, 18.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They had those caps, you know, and they had guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they were telling us what's happening, how they are fighting the Germans, they have killed a lot of Germans, and the Germans are coming with tanks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They're fighting them like a real army, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] from that bunker, we had to go, too, because they put this house on fire, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And going back to the Warsaw Ghetto-- kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "To this very day, I feel that it's like I have witnessed a part of Jewish history, a very important, a vital part of Jewish history, because I think that it has given dignity, courage.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, they always say that we went like lambs to slaughter, but we did not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this was something, that it was against all odds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Poles would not help the Jews with weapons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews were on their own to try to-- it was underground, they tried to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had to pay a lot of money for every gun they got.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think they fought against such odds for six weeks, that the Germans-- there were  a lot of Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm repeating myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans rode tanks, you understand that?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
